Dispassion is positive. It looks negative to those who are in pravritti (outgoing mind).
<br>Q: Is it a good feeling, it really feels good?
<br>A: Yes. Your attachment is your pain. If attachment is not there, peace. <span class=date>7/19/77</span>
You hold an apple in your hand and in your mind. An enlightened being holds an apple in his hand and not in his mind. <span class=date>8/7/77</span>
